{"title":"手把手教你搭建个人博客 — GitHub篇","uid":"da152832baa1aff4feefe88d8b9a71d6","slug":"手把手教你搭建个人博客-Github","date":"2021-05-13T13:43:26.000Z","updated":"2023-03-20T14:28:53.655Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/手把手教你搭建个人博客-Github.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/03/19/ppYT8r4.png","content":"<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>博客</strong>，最早诞生于1997年Userland公司CEO Dave Winer运行的Scripting News，至今已经存在超过20年。</p></blockquote>\n<p>搭建博客的框架有很多，例如：<strong>HEXO</strong>、<strong>WordPress</strong>、<strong>Hugo</strong>、<strong>VuePress</strong>等，都属于开源框架，成本低廉，利用GitHub仓库甚至连域名都不需要购买，即可让他人访问。</p>\n<p>本期主要讲述GitHub + Hexo搭建个人博客，分为上、中、下三个部分，之后我会把博客部署到国内云服务器上，届时再写一篇有关服务器部署的博客。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s3.ax1x.com/2021/03/18/6g0RKA.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"注册账号\"><a href=\"#注册账号\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注册账号\"></a>注册账号</h2><p>进入<a href=\"https://github.com/\">Github</a>官网，点击右上角的<a href=\"https://github.com/join?ref_cta=Sign+up&ref_loc=header+logged+out&ref_page=/&source=header-home\">Sign up</a></p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">提示</p>\n<p><p>GitHub首页在两年间多次改版迭代，但是整体布局始终没改，图片截取时间较早，仅供参考</p>\n</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/03/11/6tj9wn.png\"></p>\n<p>跳转到注册页面，按照下图所示，填写 <strong>Username</strong>、<strong>Email address</strong>、<strong>Password</strong>，点击 <strong>Create account</strong> 即可。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/03/11/6N9z9I.png\"></p>\n<p>接下来会跳转到<strong>调查问卷</strong>页面，节约时间直接<strong>跳过</strong>，然后Github会提示你去邮箱验证刚刚注册的账号。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/03/11/6NEHG4.png\"></p>\n<p>登录邮箱，找到邮件 <strong>[GitHub] Please verify your email address</strong>，点击绿色按钮，验证电子邮箱，自动跳转到Github，账号就注册完成了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/03/11/6Nmymn.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"创建仓库\"><a href=\"#创建仓库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建仓库\"></a>创建仓库</h2><p>点击右上角头像，选择下拉弹框中的 Your Repositories 你的仓库，点击绿色按钮 New 新建。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/03/11/6N1C7j.png\"></p>\n<p>按照下图所示，输入<strong>仓库名</strong>，其他的我就不细说了，看图即可。</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">特别注意</p>\n<p><strong>注意：仓库名必须是用户名 格式如下：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">所有者&#x2F;用户名.github.io  例如：xiaoming&#x2F;xiaoming.githubo.io</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>用户名不能带有大写字母！！！ 否则后续访问github.io会出现404问题</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">例如： Advictoriamn1&#x2F;Advictoriamn1.github.io | XIAOMING&#x2F;XIAOMING.github.io</code></pre>\n\n\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/03/11/6NaiE8.png\"></p>\n<p>填好后，点击 Create repository 按钮创建仓库，一个名为<strong>Advictoriamn1.github.io</strong>的仓库就建好了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"下载-Git\"><a href=\"#下载-Git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下载 Git\"></a>下载 Git</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><em>本文不推荐任何可视化工具，可视化虽然很便捷，但是也失去了深入学习的机会，而且Git直接输入命令比可视化快得多</em></p></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>首先进入<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/downloads\">GIT工具</a>下载页面，点击Windows（根据自己的电脑系统决定），浏览器会自动下载Git。</li>\n<li>点击安装包，默认不需要改动，直接下一步到完成即可。</li>\n<li>回到桌面，右击鼠标，出现Git Bash Here就代表Git工具已经安装成功。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"上传README-md\"><a href=\"#上传README-md\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"上传README.md\"></a>上传README.md</h2><p><em><strong>测试本地计算机与Github服务器是否连接成功，只有连接成功才能上传Hexo静态文件。</strong></em></p>\n<p><em>Git工具使用指南（阮一峰大佬的博客）：<a href=\"http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2014/06/git_remote.html\">http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2014/06/git_remote.html</a></em></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/03/18/62p5jK.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"常见问题🐞\"><a href=\"#常见问题🐞\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"常见问题🐞\"></a>常见问题🐞</h2><div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">常见问题</p>\n<p><p><em><strong>为什么打不开Github？为什么使用Git上传文件会超时报错？</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>Github服务器位于美国，可能出现连接超时的问题，请百度host自行修改，本文不再赘述。（有能力的可以选择梯子，更加便捷）</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>为什么收不到Github发送的验证电子邮件？</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>请尝试使用QQ邮箱注册，163邮箱将github.com加入白名单（2021年已不存在此问题）</strong></em></p>\n</p>\n</div>\n","text":" 博客，最早诞生于1997年Userland公司CEO Dave Winer运行的Scripting News，至今已经存在超过20年。 搭建博客的框架有很多，例如：HEXO、WordPress、Hu...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.4k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Hexo.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"GitHub","slug":"GitHub","count":1,"path":"api/tags/GitHub.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E8%B4%A6%E5%8F%B7\"><span class=\"toc-text\">注册账号</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">创建仓库</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD-Git\"><span class=\"toc-text\">下载 Git</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0README-md\"><span class=\"toc-text\">上传README.md</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%F0%9F%90%9E\"><span class=\"toc-text\">常见问题🐞</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"洛安奕然","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/03/19/ppYN7sH.jpg","link":"/","description":"STAY HUNGRY STAY FOOLISH <br /> <p>求知若饥，虚心若愚</p>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/TriDiamond","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"https://weibo.com/u/73189